  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Scope:</u></p><ul><li>Do Tender</li><li>Prepare Quotation</li><li>Prepare Contract, VO and Final Account</li><li>Compare Costing with Purchaser</li><li>Submit Claims</li><li>Budget Controlling</li><li>Breakdown Final Claim and Financial Statement</li></ul><p><u>Job Requirement: </u></p><ul><li>To have at least 5 years experience in Cladding & Facade works will be preferred </li><li>To have a Degree in Civil Engineering/Quantity Surveying/Construction Management </li><li>Able to work under fast-paced environment </li><li>Have good communication skills</li><li>Familiar with Microsoft Office (Excel, Word, Outlook, etc.)</li></ul><p>Kindly email us your resume to lokpteltd@gmail.com.</p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>",
